# Authentication Patterns

## BetterAuth Integration
- Use BetterAuth for authentication
- Implement proper session management
- Handle authentication state correctly
- Use server-side authentication checks

## Security Best Practices
- Validate all user inputs
- Implement proper CSRF protection
- Use secure session management
- Handle authentication errors gracefully

## Component Patterns
- Create reusable auth components
- Implement proper loading states
- Handle authentication redirects
- Use proper TypeScript types for auth state

## API Security
- Protect API routes with authentication
- Implement proper authorization checks
- Use middleware for auth validation
- Handle token refresh properly